'''STIR射控雷達'''是[[泰雷茲集團|泰雷茲集團]]設計的一種中遠程[[射控雷達|射控雷達系統]]，主要用於電光跟踪和飛彈照明<ref>{{cite web |title=Stir – Tracking and illumination radar |publisher=[[Thales_Group|Thales Group]] |url=https://www.thalesgroup.com/en/stir-tracking-and-illumination-radar |access-date=2020-11-04 |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230154037/https://www.thalesgroup.com/en/stir-tracking-and-illumination-radar |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|first=Martin|last=Streetly|year=2005|title=Jane's Radar and Electronic Warfare Systems 17th Edition|publisher=[[Jane's_Information_Group|Janes Information Group]]|isbn=978-0710627049|ref=harv}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|authorlink=:en:Norman Friedman|first=Norman|last=Friedman|title= The Naval Institute guide to world naval weapon systems 1997–1998|year=1997|publisher=Naval Institute Press|isbn=9781557502681|ref=harv}}</ref>。

